'''2020年危地马拉滑坡灾害'''（{{lang-es|deslizamiento de tierra en San Cristobal Verapaz de 2020}}）发生于该国[[上维拉帕斯省|上维拉帕斯省]][[圣克里斯托瓦尔贝拉帕斯|圣克里斯托瓦尔贝拉帕斯]]市境内，[[颶風伊塔|颶風伊塔]]期间。由[[山体滑坡|山体滑坡]]形成的两个[[泥石流|泥石流]]埋葬了该市的玛雅族村庄{{link-es|凯哈村|Quejá}}（或译克哈村）<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-storm-eta-guatemala-survivors/guatemala-mayan-villagers-tell-of-harrowing-escape-from-deadly-landslide-idUKKBN27P1EQ |title=Guatemala Mayan villagers tell of harrowing escape from deadly landslide |accessdate=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115023639/https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-storm-eta-guatemala-survivors/guatemala-mayan-villagers-tell-of-harrowing-escape-from-deadly-landslide-idUKKBN27P1EQ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，3000村民步行逃难至邻村Santa Elena。<ref name=NYTms />
