灾害致使数十至150个房屋被埋，目前预估至少125人死亡，3人遗体被发现，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://elperiodico.com.gt/nacionales/2020/11/06/rescate-en-queja-ejercito-localizo-tres-cadaveres-en-el-lugar-del-deslave3/ |title=Rescate en Quejá: Ejército localizó tres cadáveres en el lugar del deslave |accessdate=2020-11-07 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113115725/https://elperiodico.com.gt/nacionales/2020/11/06/rescate-en-queja-ejercito-localizo-tres-cadaveres-en-el-lugar-del-deslave3/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=NYTms>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/07/world/americas/guatemala-mudslide-storm-eta.html |title=Guatemala Rescuers Search for Scores of People Buried in Mudslide Caused by Eta |accessdate=2020-11-07 |archive-date=2020-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219102615/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/07/world/americas/guatemala-mudslide-storm-eta.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>估计至少50人在被埋的房屋中，1500人亟待救援。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.telesurtv.net/news/guatemala-cifra-muertos-lluvias-eta-20201106-0002.html |title=Presidente de Guatemala confirma más de 50 muertos por Eta |accessdate=2020-11-07 |archive-date=2020-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122191201/https://www.telesurtv.net/news/guatemala-cifra-muertos-lluvias-eta-20201106-0002.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

